quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,Tareef Allah ke liye hai jisne apne banday par yeh kitaab nazil ki aur ismein koi tedh na rakkhi
  18,2,"Theek theek seedhi baat kehne wali kitaab, taa-ke woh logon ko khuda ke sakht azaab se khabardar karde, aur iman laa kar neik amal karne walon ko khush khabri de de ke unke liye accha ajar hai"
  18,3,Jismein woh hamesha rahenge
  18,4,Aur un logon ko dara de jo kehte hain ke Allah ne kisi ko beta banaya hai
  18,5,"Is baat ka na unhein koi ilam hai aur na unke baap dada ko tha. Badi baat hai jo unke mooh se nikalti hai, woh mehaz jhoot bakhte hain"
  18,6,"Accha, to (aey Muhammad), shayad tum inke peechey gham ke marey apni jaan kho dene waley ho agar ye is taleem par iman na laye"
  18,7,Waqiya ye hai ke yeh jo kuch sar-o-samaan bhi zameen par hai isko humne zameen ki zeenat banaya hai taa-ke in logon ko aazmayein inmein kaun behtar amal karne wala hai
  18,8,Aakhir e kaar is sab ko hum ek chatiyal maidan bana dene waley hain
  18,9,Kya tum samajhte ho ke ghaar (cave) aur katbe (inscription) waley hamari koi badi ajeeb nisaniyon mein se thay
  18,10,"Jab woh chandh nawjawan ghaar mein panaah guzeen huey aur unhon ne kaha “aey parwardigar, humko apni rehmat e khaas se nawaz aur hamara maamla durust karde”"
  18,11,To humne unhein usi ghaar mein thapak kar saal ha saal ke liye gehri neend sula diya
  18,12,Phir humne unhein uthaya taa-ke dekhein unke do girohon mein se kaun apni muddat e qayaam ka theek shumar karta hai